t therapy — coaching only. Always show crisis resources: 988, Crisis Text Line (741741), SAMHSA (1-800-662-4357).\nDesign: Inter font, #FBFAF9 background, #2C808C teal accent, #272C35 dark text, rounded cards, minimal borders.\nData Types: User (name, email, timezone, primary_mode, goals, coaching_style, onboarding_completed, subscription_tier, is_admin, sobriety_start_date, recovery fields), DailyCheckIn, ChatConversation, ChatMessage, JournalEntry, Milestone, GuidedPath, PathStep, UserPathEnrollment, Resource, SavedResource, SubscriptionPlan, Workplace, BillingHistory, PaymentMethod, NotificationPreference, RelapseEvent.\nTiers: Free (journal, check-ins, AI chat trial, core resources), Pro $19/mo (full chat, all paths, full library), Elite $49/mo (executive content, priority support). Workplace-sponsored = Pro access.\nPages:\nindex — Hero (\"AI-Powered Personal Coaching\"), How It Works, Coaching Modes (Life & Health, Professional, Emotional, Recovery, Executive), Pricing, Workplace section, Footer. Signup + Sales popups.\ndashboard — Greeting, daily check-in card, AI chat preview, current path progress, recent journal entries, Recovery Dashboard (sober counter, milestones, mood chart — visible if primary_mode = Recovery), crisis resources always visible.\nchat — Two-panel: conversation list sidebar + active chat panel. New Topic button, message input, crisis panel, history drawer.\njournal — Journal tab (entries list, new entry, AI reflection, delete), Milestones tab (achievements, recovery timeline).\npaths-resources — Guided Paths tab (filter by mode/tier), Resource Library tab (search, filter, safety resources always free).\nsettings — Tabs: Profile, Coaching, Privacy & Data, Security, Notifications, Workplace, Subscription, Admin Dashboard (admin only: analytics + manage paths/resources/plans/workplaces).\nreset_pw — Reset password form.\n404 — Not found page.\nOnboarding (shown on dashboard if onboarding_completed = false, non-dismissible):\nName + timezone\nSelect coaching mode (Recovery adds Step 5)\nGoals\nCoaching style → marks onboarding_completed = true\nRecovery details (sobriety date, substance, triggers, high-risk times, motivation, alerts toggle)\nPrivacy: All personal data owner-only. Employers see anonymized aggregates only. Admins cannot view individual user data. is_admin set server-side only.","welcome_greeting":"Welcome to Unclouded, your private AI-powered coaching app—I'm here to help you build, refine, and iterate every part of it."},"first_times":{"component_library":false},"font_tokens":{"default":"Inter"},"allow_iframe":"DENY","app_language":"en_us","color_tokens":{"text":{"default":"rgba(39, 44, 52, 1)"},"alert":{"default":"rgba(243, 155, 22, 1)"},"primary":{"default":"rgba(44, 127, 140, 1)"},"success":{"default":"rgba(66, 148, 118, 1)"},"surface":{"default":"rgba(255, 255, 255, 1)"},"background":{"default":"rgba(251, 250, 249, 1)"},"destructive":{"default":"rgba(221, 56, 44, 1)"},"primary_contrast":{"default":"rgba(255, 255, 255, 1)"}},"use_sendgrid":true,"feature_flags":{"ppe":true},"sitemap_pages":"[]","spinner_color":"rgba(227, 227, 229, 1)","style_version":5,"bubble_version":32,"color_swatches":{"0":"rgba(3, 180, 198, 1)","1":"rgba(58, 77, 143, 1)","2":"rgba(50, 67, 128, 1)","3":"rgba(9, 23, 71, 1)","4":"rgba(153, 153, 153, 1)","5":"rgba(214, 39, 85, 1)","6":"rgba(255, 255, 255, 1)"},"default_styles":{"Icon":"Icon_default_","Link":"Link_inline_","Text":"Text_body_","Group":"Group_transparent_","Image":"Image_default_","Input":"Input_default_","Popup":"Popup_dialog_","Button":"Button_primary_","Checkbox":"Checkbox_default_","Dropdown":"Dropdown_default_","MultiLineInput":"Input_multiline_","RepeatingGroup":"RepeatingGroup_list_"},"exposes_wf_api":true,"exposes_get_api":true,"ai_generated_app":true,"comments_viewers":{"bTHtI":{"1737123517443x175520695552991330":true}},"default_icon_set":"material","expose_text_tags":true,"font_tokens_user":{"default":{"bTHFv":{"description":"font variable fro